{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "**Project:** `16-ble-beacon`", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "**What it does:**", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "Turns the TFL_CONNECT_2 board into a **BLE advertising beacon** using the FC41D Wi-Fi+BLE module (connected via UART9).", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "The firmware:", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "1. Powers on the FC41D, disables echo (`ATE0`), and initializes BLE mode", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "2. Sets the device name to **\"CCoreAIBLE\"**", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "3. Builds a 25-byte advertising payload with:", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "   - Standard BLE flags (LE General Discoverable)", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "   - Manufacturer Specific data containing **\"Hello from CCoreAI\"**", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "4. Starts advertising at **100 ms interval**", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "5. Blinks the **green LED at 1 Hz** while the beacon is running", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "6. Prints a status trace every 10 s on UART7 (115200 baud): `[STATUS] beacon running — advertising CCoreAIBLE / Hello from CCoreAI`", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
{"type": "text", "stream": "stdout", "text": "**Error states:**", "ts": "2026-05-18T15:19:07+00:00", "time": "18:19:07"}
